TA;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "both of which together consist of four and twenty of those divisions; each of them, when they are of equal length, consisting of twelve such divisions;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA;) [also termed"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saAEapN falakiy~apN", "text_ar": "سَاعَةٌ فَلَكِيَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "("}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an astronomical hour; fifteen"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "darajaAt", "text_ar": "دَرَجَات"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of time; sixty minutes of time;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ") because"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sAEp", "text_ar": "ساعة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "alone is often used in a vague sense, as meaning what is termed"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saAEapN zamaAniy~apN", "text_ar": "سَاعَةٌ زَمَانِيَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; i. e.]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a time of night"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of day:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "but used absolutely by the Arabs as meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a time; a while; a space,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "period; an indefinite"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "short"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "time;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a little while;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "short"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "little portion,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "division,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "space,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "period,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the night"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the day:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Als~aAEapu", "text_ar": "السَّاعَةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pre-"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 1468}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sent time:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K:) pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saAEaAtN", "text_ar": "سَاعَاتٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saAEN", "text_ar": "سَاعٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, Msb, K,) [or the latter is rather a coll. gen. n. of which"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sAEp", "text_ar": "ساعة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is the n. un.,] and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "siwaAEN", "text_ar": "سِوَاعٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (Msb.) It is used unrestricted in the Kur [vii. 32 and in other places], where it is said,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laA yasotaA^oxiruwna saAEapF", "text_ar": "لَا يَسْتَاْخِرُونَ سَاعَةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They will not remain behind"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "for a time,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "any while,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the shortest time:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "they shall not seek to remain behind,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "by reason of intense terror. (Bd.) And so in a trad., where it is said,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mano raAHa fiY Als~aAEapi AlA^uwlaY", "text_ar": "مَنْ رَاحَ فِى السَّاعَةِ الاُولَى"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Whoso goeth in the first time;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "not in the first astronomical"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sAEp", "text_ar": "ساعة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", for then it would necessarily mean that he who should come in the latter part thereof would be on a par with the former person, which is not the case. (Msb.) ["}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saAEapF", "text_ar": "سَاعَةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies, as shown above,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "For,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "during, an hour:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "awhile; for a little while; during a short time;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as in the phrase,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jalasotu Einodaka saAEapF", "text_ar": "جَلَسْتُ عِنْدَكَ سَاعَةً"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I sat with thee,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "at thine abode, for a little while,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "during a short time."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) [And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fiY saAEapK", "text_ar": "فِى سَاعَةٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "In a short time: in a moment."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Als~aAEapa", "text_ar": "السَّاعَةَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Now: just now: this moment."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saAEatay^i*K", "text_ar": "سَاعَتَيِذٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Then; at that time:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in that hour."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mu*o saAEapNK", "text_ar": "مُذْ سَاعَةٌٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A little while ago;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in the first time near to us:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Anf", "text_ar": "انف"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ":) or this signifies"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Als~aAEapa", "text_ar": "السَّاعَةَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[expl. above]. (Zj, T and M in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Anf", "text_ar": "انف"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) [And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mino saAEatihi", "text_ar": "مِنْ سَاعَتِهِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "At the moment thereof; instantly."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "Hence,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sam~a saAEapK", "text_ar": "سَمَّ سَاعَةٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "An instantaneous poison."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Als~aAEapu", "text_ar": "السَّاعَةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also signifies (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The resurrection;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K, TA;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the raising of mankind for the reckoning;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also termed"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Als~aAEapu AlkuboraY", "text_ar": "السَّاعَةُ الكُبْرَى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Er-Rághib, B:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the time thereof:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) because of the quickness with which its reckoning will be accomplished: (TA:) or because it will come suddenly upon mankind, in a moment, and all creatures will die at one cry. (Zj, Az, TA.) Hence, in the Kur [liv. 1],"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aiqotarabati Als~aAEapu", "text_ar": "اِقْتَرَبَتِ السَّاعَةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The resurrection"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the time thereof"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "hath drawn nigh."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Jel, TA.) And [in vii. 186 and lxxix. 42,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yasoA^aluwnaka Eani Als~aAEapi", "text_ar": "يَسْاَلُونَكَ عَنِ السَّاعَةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They ask thee concerning the resurrection"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the time thereof"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (Bd, Jel, TA.) And [in xxxi. last verse and xliii. 85,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Einodahu Eilomu Als~aAEapi", "text_ar": "عِنْدَهُ عِلْمُ السَّاعَةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "With Him is the knowledge of the resurrection,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the time thereof."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd, Jel.) ―         -b3-  Also (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The death of one generation;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "termed, for distinction,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Als~aAEapu AlwusoTaY", "text_ar": "السَّاعَةُ الوُسْطَى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": as in the saying of Mohammad, when he saw 'AbdAllah Ibn-Uneys,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_ino yaTulo Eumoru h`*aA AlgulaAmi lamo yamuto", "text_ar": "اـِنْ يَطُلْ عُمْرُ هٰذَا الغُلَامِ لَمْ يَمُتْ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hat~aY taquwma Als~aAEapu", "text_ar": "حَتَّى تَقُومَ السَّاعَةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "If the life of this boy last long, he will not die until the death of the generation shall come to pass"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: accordingly it is said that he was the last that died of the Companions. (Er-Rághib, B.) ―         -b4-  Also (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The death of any man;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "termed, for distinction,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Als~aAEapu AlS~ugoraY", "text_ar": "السَّاعَةُ الصُّغْرَى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": as in the Kur [vi. 31],"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qado xasira A@l~a*ayna ka*~abuwA biliqaA='i", "text_ar": "قَدْ خَسِرَ ا@لَّذَينَ كَذَّبُوا بِلِقَا=ءِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A@ll~`hi Hat~aY A_i*aA jaA='atohumu A@ls~aA`Eapu bagotapF", "text_ar": "ا@للّٰهِ حَتَّى اـِذَا جَا=ءَتْهُمُ ا@لسَّاٰعَةُ بَغْتَةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They have suffered loss who disbelieved in,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "denied as false, the meeting with God until, when death came to them suddenly"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (Er-Rághib, B) ―         -b5-  Also (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Difficulty, distress,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "affliction;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and so ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Als~aAEu", "text_ar": "السَّاعُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) ―         -b6-  And (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Distance,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "remoteness."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)       -A2-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saAy^iEN", "text_ar": "سَايِعٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "."}], "source_refs": ["TA", "S", "K", "Msb", "Bd"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}